    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = v0
    tmp = (v2 + wp.sin((v2 + 0.98 - v2 + 0.94)))
    v1 = (v0 + wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.62)))
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.24)))
